content:
Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards. Manage reports and dashboards on Analytics Home.

Reports:

* Build a Report
* Customize Report Views in the Run Page
* Updating Multiple Report Fields Inline
* Filter Report Data
* Schedule and Subscribe to Reports
* Get Notified When Report Conditions Are Met
* Attach Files to Report Subscriptions

Get Notified When Report Conditions Are Met

Set report conditions so that recipients are notified when a total in your Salesforce report reaches a meaningful threshold.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS

Available in: Lightning Experience, Essentials, Group, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
To subscribe to reports: Subscribe to Reports
To specify who runs the report in a report subscription: Subscribe to Reports: Set Running User
title: Get Notified When Report Conditions Are Met
